{"tid":1235740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蕭若元 : 7月22日後香港和中国「呢兩個地方唔存在」","createTime":"2019-06-17T08:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T03:25:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"16c074ae2a28ea63ddfb784cf6cc721a92965c6d","tid":1235740,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:36:43.000Z","msg":"時事評論人蕭若元宣佈，7 月 22 日後，不會再評論香港及中國的時事及經濟事務，形容「呢兩個地方唔存在」，並指這是兒子蕭定一的要求，但未有再進一步透露詳情。<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元又表示，他評論中港時政二十年，「要講嘅嘢都差唔多講晒，講落去都係重複」，之後會將節目名稱由《最新蕭析》改為《退休蕭析》，議題改為旅遊、八卦嘢、哲學、人生、外國時事等。他又再三感謝聽眾多年支持。<br />\n<br />\n蕭定一：想做「簡單愛國商人」<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元之子蕭定一為 HMV 數碼中國集團主席，在大中華地區經營影視及藝人經理業務，HMV 數碼中國旗下藝人有鄭欣宜、周柏豪、連詩雅、張智霖、王宗堯等。<br />\n<br />\n去年九月，《大公報》報道指蕭氏父子是「本土民主前線」的「幕後金主」，蕭定一曾發表聲明回應，指自己「作為一個在香港及中國地區經營文化產業的生意人，對參與香港任何政治活動絕無興趣」，又表明「我最重視的是如何令中國文化產業繼續向好，為公司股東謀求最大利益，做一個簡單的愛國商人，請不要再將政治與我拉上任何關係」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E8%95%AD%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-%E8%95%AD%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%83%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%887%E6%9C%8822%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2595%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E8%2595%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%25887%25E6%259C%258822%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&d=goC%2B%2BwCxwRgX8SEPTes0uwqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=b162f2b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%2595%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582-%25E8%2595%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%2585%2583%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%25887%25E6%259C%258822%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%2F&h=16ab0588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E8%95%AD%E5%AE%9A%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82-%E8%95%AD%E8%8B%A5%E5%85%83%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%887%E6%9C%8822%E6%97%A5%E5%BE%8C%E4%B8%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B/</a>"},{"pid":"a8275833c0e8b383b4fc1249f9ff56389e9e53df","tid":1235740,"uid":54181,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9cbedc7127a22781515ec7ba622ef3c54a2b0044","tid":1235740,"uid":100337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8275833c0e8b383b4fc1249f9ff56389e9e53df","tid":1235740,"uid":54181,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:37:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:38:59.000Z","msg":"old news"},{"pid":"ba2e003a7151a3622d5a389b4dd6b76b73a2baab","tid":1235740,"uid":188264,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:39:03.000Z","msg":"2017/5/19 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b036c7e29140dc18e16635c45a57de71a0a30c","tid":1235740,"uid":231040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"【反送中過後】屌你老味!!! 下星期就係《國歌法》二讀嘞....<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPCuCS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPCuCS</a>"},{"pid":"923f09cd8e02df4560678d4af3bedbe27e89a1a9","tid":1235740,"uid":17510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T08:54:27.000Z","msg":"時事評論人蕭若元宣佈，7 月 22 日後，不會再評論香港及中國的時事及經濟事務，形容「呢兩個地方唔存在」，並指這是兒子蕭定一的要求<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呀仔：咪撚再燈啦老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead